    explanation:"Certificate types: DV (Domain Validation) = automated, proves you control the domain (seconds-hours). Let's Encrypt issues DV certs. OV (Organization Validation) = human review (1-3 days), company name shown in cert details. EV (Extended Validation) = most rigorous (days-weeks), business license, officer auth, 3+ years in business. EV green bar removed by Chrome/Firefox in 2019.",
